The perfect combination of lip colour and care, these tints will keep your pout soft with rich intense pigment. Rich in natural butters & oils this makeup + skincare hybrid is the hydrating lip tint you’ll love to wear.

Benefits :
- Delivers intense hydration
- Gives your lips a healthy dose of colour and shine
- Moisturises your pucker for a healthy, plump look
Lightweight and non-sticky, comforting formula
Can be worn on your lips, cheeks and eyes
Restores softness and elasticity

Nude Pink (I am Beautiful) A subtle, nude pink lip tint that you can wear from AM to PM and flaunt every day.

Perfect Pink (I am Love) A pretty pink liquid lip balm to brighten up your everyday look and give you the perfect pout.

We work. We grow. We won’t stop!

In midst of a chaotic production, delayed shipments from vendors, overlooking 500-800 daily dispatches, planning inventory and still keeping the team motivated to function. We still managed to launch another mini-extension to our Arcana’25 edit! For the first time I could feel the burn! I could feel the exhaustion- even yet, we somehow pulled it through! 

This is what makes us ♥️ This is what moves us!#TeamJenn @thelabel.jenn
